[
    {
        "Key": 1,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "经历些小挫折后，“心率实验”陷入了停滞状态。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 2,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "芙提雅和研发团队忙着思考新的方向，倒是给了我和妮塔许多“自由活动”的时间。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我走在前往妮塔房间的路上，心里一直酝酿着开导她的话语。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "倒不是担心她因为这点小事就失去信心，我反而更忧心，她会给自己太大压力。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "毕竟这是她第一次参与研发工作，想要全力以赴做到极致也是人之常情。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但打开房门后，我想象中的，带着焦虑苦闷表情的妮塔并未出现。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她正把脑袋搁桌边，目光诡异地凝视着在面前的提拉米苏上，神色更带着几分……兴奋？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "虽然这份甜点散发着浓郁的咖啡香气，金黄松软的手指饼干排列整齐，面上的可可粉也细腻诱人。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但它“餐厅常驻”的属性，让人提不起任何对它的兴趣……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "当然，妮塔除外，只要是免费的美食，她都爱吃。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "口水都快流下来了……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我凑到妮塔旁边，彼此的脸几乎要贴到一起。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "哇啊啊啊，分析员。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "妮塔吓得一扑腾，整个人连带着椅子就要往左侧翻下去。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "b-1",
        "Flag": "b-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "b-1-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "拉住妮塔",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "情急之下，我下意识抓住她的手臂。她反应极快，顺势一个转身，整个人便跌入我的怀抱。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "待她抬头时，我才注意到她鼻尖不知何时沾上了一点奶油。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "别动，这里脏了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "意识到自己的失态，妮塔迅速将脸凑了过来，乖乖等着我的指腹靠近。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "就这么一瞬，绯色在她的脸颊上快速扩散着。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "b-2",
        "Flag": "b-2",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "b-2-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "蹭掉奶油",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在我拿起纸巾，清理掉手上那点污渍时，妮塔露出了不舍又欲言又止的表情。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你不会连这点都舍不得吧？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "没有，没有舍不得……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她装作不经意地转开目光，却还是忍不住追随着那团沾了奶油的纸巾，看它画出一道完美的弧线，轻巧地落入垃圾桶。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "难道说，你最近是在……瘦身？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "没有啊，怎么可能，我身材匀称着呢！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 28,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "妮塔火速撩起衣服，用傲人的马甲线证明自己所言非虚。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "提拉米苏一口没动，米粒大的奶油都馋得不行，这要吃不吃的样子不像你啊……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 30,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不是要吃不吃，是绝对不吃，我正在克制自己的欲望！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 31,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "难道在我不知道的时候，提拉米苏变成限量供应了？这事儿我去和后勤部说说吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 32,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "队员们这么辛苦，总不能想吃块蛋糕都抠抠搜搜的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 33,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "别……别！分析员，我不是那个意思。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 34,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "看到我想联系后勤部，妮塔连忙缠住了我的手臂，再把我的手和终端一起摁回了口袋。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 35,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那你的意思是？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 36,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这几天，我从心率实验失败的结果中悟出了一些道理。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 37,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我——是个贪心的女人！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 38,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "妮塔将手放在心口，语气里带着几分郑重，颇有几分苦情的意味。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 39,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在空气都沉默了三秒钟后，一丝疑惑浮现上妮塔的脸。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 40,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析员，你不反驳我一下吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 41,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "反驳？我觉得妮塔对自我认知很清晰啊。昨天不就是直到早上，才肯放我……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 42,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "还没说完，我的嘴就被妮塔捂得严严实实，足足封了两层。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 43,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不是那种贪心！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 44,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "或许是怕我再列举这些令她脸红的“罪状”，她连忙把事情一股脑倒了出来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 45,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "之前心率实验的时候，分析员准备了那么多都没让我的心跳到达理论值……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 46,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "都是因为我吃着锅里的，望着盆里的，总是奢求更好的！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 47,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "如果我从现在开始控制饮食！那么不久后，我就会像一头饥肠辘辘的野兽，满足于一切食物，哪怕是西兰花也能让我兴奋。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 48,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你说对吧，分……分分分析员！你怎么把我的提拉米苏吃掉了？！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 49,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "就在妮塔念念叨叨时，提拉米苏已经被我三口吞下。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 50,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这令人熟悉的味道果然让人激不起任何兴趣，但用来垫垫肚子还是绰绰有余。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 51,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "近在眼前的食物就这么没了，克制多时的“野兽小姐”有什么想法吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 52,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我的话让妮塔陷入沉思，手指轻托着下巴思索着，却又因为理不清头绪，无奈地拍了拍脑袋。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 53,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "是不是一点想法都没有？因为你也知道……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 54,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这样的甜点，每天都能在餐厅冷藏区里找到，口感和预期分毫不差，毫无惊喜可言。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 55,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "就算是克制欲望很久的野兽，也只会把西兰花视为生存所需。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 56,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "真正能让内心震颤的，永远是腥气十足，鲜美多汁的第一口肉。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 57,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "所以，对妮塔来说，美味的肉代表着什么呢？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 58,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "可我已经得到很多了……分析员的陪伴还有花不完「随心兑」……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 59,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "《30天成为富豪》里还说过，贪婪者总是一贫如洗！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 60,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "妮塔郁闷地坐回椅子上，手掌拖住半边脸颊。从苦闷的表情中可以看出她内心正蒙受着谴责。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "b-3",
        "Flag": "b-3",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 61,
        "Flag": "b-3-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "开导妮塔",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 62,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我单膝跪到她的身前，把她的双手裹在手心里，举至唇边，轻轻落下一吻。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 63,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那是因为人们总是染指自己不配拥有的东西。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 64,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但你得到的那些……姑且算作我的心意吧，在我看来都不算什么。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 65,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "因为妮塔还值得拥有更好的，能让你幸福到心跳加速的东西。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 66,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "抬头望去时，我在她泛着水光的眸中，撞见了自己的倒影。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 67,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析员这么说的话……我有一点点想法了！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 68,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "沉思片刻后，妮塔转身埋首于书桌前，笔尖在纸上飞舞，几乎要擦出火星。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 69,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "很快，她就完成了画作并得意地举到了我的眼前。",
